           move      zero                 to   w-tot-cli-tiv          .
           move      zero                 to   w-tot-cli-tot          .
           move      zero                 to   w-tot-cli-tvo          .
           move      zero                 to   w-tot-cli-tvi          .
           move      srt-sgl-vpf          to   w-tot-cli-vpf          .
           move      srt-dec-vpf          to   w-tot-cli-dpf          .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
